                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - D
                   ====================================

                              Death Or Glory
                              ==============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Immunity" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37788,201) ZXAMPoke(37912,201) ZXAMPoke(38117,201) ZXAMPoke(38189,201)"}                37788,201:37912,201:38117,201:38189,201

                         This POKE seems to give immunity/infinite shields, but
                         it was stated as being for 255 lives. I left it running
                         for a while and I was still alive (in the game! hehe),
                         so you'll have to make your own mind up I guess...

                                                                    Rastan.
